<h2 class="boxed">
	<span style="color:#000000;font-family:Arial;">16 June 2012 - Apache Mahout 0.7 released</span>
</h2>
<p>
	<span style="color:#000000;font-family:Arial;">Apache Mahout has reached version 0.7. All developers are encouraged to begin using version
  0.7. Highlights include:</span>
</p>
<ul>
	<li>
		<span style="color:#000000;font-family:Arial;">Outlier removal capability in K-Means, Fuzzy K, Canopy and Dirichlet Clustering</span>
	</li>
	<li>
		<span style="color:#000000;font-family:Arial;">New Clustering implementation for K-Means, Fuzzy K, Canopy and Dirichlet using Cluster Classifiers</span>
	</li>
	<li>
		<span style="color:#000000;font-family:Arial;">Collections and Math api consolidated</span>
	</li>
	<li>
		<span style="color:#000000;font-family:Arial;">(Complementary) Naive Bayes refactored and cleaned</span>
	</li>
	<li>
		<span style="color:#000000;font-family:Arial;">Watchmaker and Old Naive Bayes dropped.</span>
	</li>
	<li>
		<span style="color:#000000;font-family:Arial;">Many bug fixes, refactorings, and other small improvements</span>
	</li>
</ul>
<p>
	<span style="color:#000000;font-family:Arial;">Changes in 0.7 are detailed in the </span><a href="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ReleaseNote.jspa?projectId=12310751&amp;version=12319261"><span style="color:#000000;font-family:Arial;">release notes</span></a><span style="color:#000000;font-family:Arial;">.</span>
</p>
<p>
